2- an interactive mode that have multiple options and have this art bellow:
    * general information like the simple mode
    * graphical representaion of the block-chain and each block's hash
    * "catch me an elephant" : the user specify an ammount (in Million dollars) and each
        time a transaction that big (or obv bigger) gets brodcasted (or verified) the user 
        gets a notification


